{
  "stem": "22979.7",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Surviving three years, and then risk my life?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Somehow, like in [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Lager, ?] I always said, maybe it will change, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We'll get an exit visa.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Was there anti-Semitism there?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Fred ?] will tell you that story, how he was the only person on the [INAUDIBLE] for the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They kicked him out, only Jew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was, then, a big trail with [INAUDIBLE] like in Russia, was the trial in Hungary, was the trial-- the accused them, innocent, and tried them, and murdered them, only because they were Jews.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It went on all over.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't raise them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't talk about that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because they had nowhere to go, [? let's see, ?] and get, you know, education.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was no-- no-- I mean, it was no good for me, as a mother, for us, us parents, to teach them of that and then be hated by the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyway they pointed at them, they are Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because the neighborhood knew we are Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we didn't have a chance to be a community, to educate our children.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we didn't have belonging to anywhere, to a group.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not too many.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1966 We were already in America. 1944-- all the 20 years, we were just asking exit visa.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because we got already a permit from the United-- from the embassy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We got the affidavit.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We could go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the Slovaks wouldn't let us go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't want us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they didn't want to let us go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] But finally, we got a permit, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In two weeks, we were in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we spent two months in Vienna waiting for the rest of the American permits.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we came March 31st to America. '66.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
